    {
      "role": "user",
      "content": "\"non-negotiable step\" is a strong way to put it. so if the environmental benefit is pretty much a fact, does that mean the arguments about it being a \"regressive tax\" on workers are just secondary concerns that we'll eventually have to deal with once the climate stuff is sorted?",
